                        <desc>
                          <locus target="#18r" facs="018"/> There is a space for the name of the bishop, but it is left unfilled.  On folio <locus target="#25v" facs="026"/>, the same thing happens with the name of the king.
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="e2">
                        <desc>
                          words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#14r" facs="014"/>);
                          and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#16v" facs="017"/>);
                          and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#37r" facs="037">  f. 37r, col. 2, line 4</locus>);
                          erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#7v #17v #22r #33v" facs="008 018 022 034"/>)
                        </desc>
